messages.message: Build is unable to parse any values for `Employment` and `Projects` from this resume and they're large sections whereas it can parse `Certifications` which is a smaller section on the left side on the bottom under Tools and Technologies
Multi column docs are not yet supported cc: @Bartosz Topolski
Not sure if this is purely because of the multicol, especially it can parse some other sections. But yeah, I can definitely add some generic CVs to multi-col benchmarks, seems like a common use-case
Should we add this to the limitations section in the docs, @jean?
